<%= wicked_pdf_stylesheet_link_tag "documents" %>
<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<!-- PAGE 1 -->
<div id="page_1" class="print-page" data-mercury="full">
	<hr><%= image_tag get_image_path, :alt => 'logo', :class => 'logo' %>
	<h2>ADVANCE COMMITMENT LEADER</h2>
	<p>The Advance Commitment Team will plan and conduct Advance Commitment Gatherings that are designed to inform and inspire parish leaders to make their sacrificial commitment prior to the majority of the parish community. The total early commitments will be announced on Commitment Weekend to show that the leadership has stepped forward and that the campaign is poised for success.</p>

	<h3>Responsibilities:</h3>

	<ul class="page_data">
		<li>Attend Leadership Team Training, Leadership Report meetings and Advance Commitment planning meetings</li>
		<li>Attend Advance Commitment Gatherings</li>
		<li>Coordinate Invitations and Gatherings with Pacesetter Gifts team</li>
		<li>Prepare an invitation list that equal to 15%-25% of the parish households</li>
		<li>Work with the Pastor and Campaign Chairs to determine times, locations and food for the gatherings</li>
		<li>Enlist a team that is based on the instructions in Tab #5, Involvement. The team will:
			<ul>
				<li>Help plan, set up, and host the gathering(s)</li>
				<li>Hand address Advance Commitment Gathering invitations</li>
				<li>Make Advance Commitment Gathering reservation phone calls</li>
				<li>After the Advance Commitment Gathering(s), send follow-up letters and or make follow-up calls</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Publicly support the campaign for the parish and arch/diocese</li>
		<li>Prayerfully consider a sacrificial financial commitment to the campaign</li>
	</ul>
	<br><br>
	<div id="date_list" class="border-box-radius">
		<h4>**MEETINGS YOU SHOULD ATTEND**</h4>

		<div class="left-column" data-mercury="full">
			<%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_trng) %><br>
			<%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_1) %><br>
			<%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_1) %><br>
			<%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_2) %><br>
			<%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_2) %><br>
			<%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_3) %><br>
			<%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_3) %><br>
			<%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.ac_host_orient) %><br>
			<%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.ac_gather_1) %><br>
			<%= formatted_date_to_tomorrow(@campaign.event.weekend_4_dates) %>
		</div>
		
		<div class="center-column" data-mercury="full">
			<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.leadership_team_trng) %><br>
			<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_1) %><br>
			<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_1) %><br>
			<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_2) %><br>
			<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_2) %><br>
			<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_3) %><br>
			<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_3) %><br>
			<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_host_orient) %><br>
			<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_gather_1) %><br>
		</div>

		<div id="list_data" class="right-column" data-mercury="full">
			<span>Leadership Team Training</span><br>
			<span>Advance Commitment Meeting #1</span><br>
			<span>Leadership Team Report Meeting #1</span><br>
			<span>Advance Commitment Meeting #2</span><br>
			<span>Leadership Team Report Meeting #2</span><br>
			Advance Commitment Meeting #3<br>
			Leadership Team Report Meeting #3<br>
			Advance Commitment Host Orientation<br>
			Advance Commitment Gathering #1<br>
			<strong>Commitment Weekend &amp; Parish-Wide Event</strong>
		</div>
	</div>
</div> <!-- END PAGE 1 -->

<!-- PAGE 2 -->
<div id="page_2" class="print-page" data-mercury="full">
	<hr><%= image_tag get_image_path, :alt => 'logo', :class => 'logo' %>
	<h2>- Timetable For Completing Your Tasks -</h2>
	<br>
	<h3><%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_trng) %><br><br>
	Leadership Team Training and Individual Team Meetings</h3>
	<br>
	<ul class="page_data" data-mercury="full">
		<li>Attend Leadership Team Training - <strong><%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.leadership_team_trng) %></strong></li>
		<li>Review your workbook and place the dates and times of the meetings you will attend on your personal calendar</li>
		<li>Attend Advance Commitment meeting #1 - <strong><%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_1) %></strong>
			<ul>
				<li>Receive details of the Advance Commitment process and strategy from your consultant</li>
				<li>Discuss and make preliminary plans for time(s), location(s) and food</li>
				<li>Review the first draft of the invitation list</li>
				<li>Discuss qualifications of enlistees:
					<ul>
						<li>Leaders in the parish</li>
						<li>Those very involved in the ministries of the parish (high ownership)</li>
						<li>Represent a broad cross section of the parish</li>
						<li>Ability to make and willingness to pray about a sacrificial commitment to the campaign</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
	</ul>
	<br><br>
	<div class="border-box">
		<h3>Between Leadership Team Training and<br>
			Report Meeting #1 on <%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_1) %>
		</h3>
		<ul class="box-data">
			<li>Enlist team members. Number based on the Involvement section in this manual</li>
			<li>Meet with other Advancement Commitment Leaders for a planning session</li>
			<li>Communicate with the Pastor and Campaign Chairs with regard to your plans</li>
			<li>Complete the first draft of the Advance Commitment Gathering invitation list</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div> <!-- END PAGE 2 -->

<!-- PAGE 3 -->
<div id="page_3" class="print-page" data-mercury="full">
	<hr><%= image_tag get_image_path, :alt => 'logo', :class => 'logo' %>
	<h2><%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_1) %></h2>
	<h3>Leadership Team Report #1 and Individual Team Meetings</h3>
	<br>
	<ul class="page_data">
		<li>Attend Leadership Team Report #1 - <strong><%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_1) %></strong>
			<ul>
				<li>Report on progress and plans for the Advance Commitment Gathering</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Attend Advance Commitment Team Meeting #2 - <strong><%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_2) %></strong>
			<ul>
				<li>Finalize plans for gatherings</li>
				<li>Dates</li>
				<li>Location</li>
				<li>Food</li>
				<li>Hosts</li>
				<li>Invitation list and invitations (the invitation comes from the pastor or parish life coordinator and is open about the purpose of the event...see sample letters Appendix B - C)
					<ol>
						<li>Review involvement progress</li>
						<li>Do we have enough people?</li>
						<li>Do we have the right people?</li>
					</ol>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
	</ul>
	<br>
	<div class="border-box">
		<h3>Between Leadership Team Report #1 and<br>
			Leadership Team Report #2 on <%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_2) %>
		</h3>
		<ul class="page_data">
			<li>Monitor Involvement</li>
			<li>Plan to attend Leadership Team Report #2, <strong><%= formatted_datetime(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_2) %></strong></li>
			<li>Call to remind entire team to attend Advance Commitment meeting #3, the night of Leadership Team Report #2, <strong><%= formatted_datetime(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_3) %></strong>, if needed to assist with hand addressing invitations</li>
			<li>Prepare to mail Advance Commitment Invitations. Things to consider:
				<ul>
					<li>Timing</li>
					<li>Hand addressing - will it be done at Advance Commitment #3 or does it need to be done sooner?</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>Depending upon the calendar, the Advance Commitment Invitation may be mailed either right before or right after Leadership Team Report #3 (at least 3 weeks prior to the first gathering)</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div> <!-- END PAGE 3 -->

<!-- PAGE 4 -->
<div id="page_4" class="print-page" data-mercury="full">
	<hr><%= image_tag get_image_path, :alt => 'logo', :class => 'logo' %>
	<h2><%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_2) %></h2>
	<h3>Leadership Team Report #2 and Individual Team Meetings</h3>
	<br>
	<ul class="page_data">
		<li>Attend Leadership Team Report #2 - <strong><%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_2) %></strong>
			<ul>
				<li>Report on progress and plans</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Attend Advance Commitment Meeting #3 - <strong><%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_mtg_3) %></strong>
			<ul>
				<li>Oversee the call assignment process (your consultant will suggest ways to conduct the assignment process)</li>
				<li>Confirm team assignments, timing, etc.</li>
				<li>Hand address Advance Commitment Invitations, if they are not already addressed</li>
				<li>Determine follow-up strategy and dates for these to take place
					<ul>
						<li>Reminder phone calls to those who attend but have not yet turned in a commitment card (Appendix F)</li>
						<li>Thank you and encouragement letters to those who attended the gatherings (two days after the gathering)</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
	</ul>
	<div class="border-box">
		<h3>Between Leadership Team Report #2 and<br>
			Leadership Team Report #3 on <%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_3) %>
		</h3>
		<ul class="page_data">
			<li>Prepare for call assignments (this may be done by you or the Campaign Administrator; ask your consultant)
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Option #1</strong> - Allow team members to select households they know well or,</li>
					<li><strong>Option #2</strong> - Divide the invitation list equally by the number of Advance Commitment Team members</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>Encourage your enlistees to attend Advance Commitment Host Orientation the night of Report Meeting #3, <strong><%= formatted_datetime(@campaign.event.ac_host_orient) %></strong>
				<ul>
					<li>Let them know that this meeting is essential</li>
					<li>Call assignments will be made (selections should be friends and people with whom they have influence)</li>
					<li>Finalize last-minute details</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>Prepare spoken and bulletin announcements. These should be general invitations to everyone in the parish and should include a request to <em>"please call the parish office to make reservations"</em> for those who wish to attend. (Appendix E) </li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div> <!-- END PAGE 4 -->

<!-- PAGE 5 -->
<div id="page_5" class="print-page" data-mercury="full">
	<hr><%= image_tag get_image_path, :alt => 'logo', :class => 'logo' %>
	<h2><%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_3) %></h2>
	<h3>Leadership Team Report #3 and Individual Team Meetings</h3>
	<br>
	<ul class="page_data">
		<li>Attend Leadership Team Report #3 - <strong><%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.leadership_team_rpt_mtg_3) %></strong>. Report on progress and plans
			<ul>
				<li>Emphasize that it is important that each Leadership Team member attend an Advance Commitment Gathering</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Attend Advance Commitment Host Orientation - <strong><%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_host_orient) %></strong>
			<ul>
				<li>Oversee the call assignment process (your consultant will suggest ways to conduct the assignment process)</li>
				<li>Review plans for Advance Commitment Gathering</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
	</ul>
	<div class="border-box">
		<h3 class="left">Following Leadership Team Report #3</h3>
		<ul class="page_data">
			<li>Mail Advance Commitment Invitations, if this has not been done</li>
			<li>Conduct/attend Advance Commitment Gathering</li>
			<li>Track attendance</li>
			<li>Oversee reservation and reminder calls</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<br>
	<h2><%= formatted_date(@campaign.event.ac_gather_1) %><br><br>
		<%= formatted_time(@campaign.event.ac_gather_1) %>
	</h2>
	<h3>Advance Commitment Gathering</h3>
	<ul class="page_data">
		<li>Plan to attend Advance Commitment Gathering</li>
	</ul>
	<div class="border-box">
		<h3>Between Advance Commitment Gathering and<br>
			Commitment Weekend on <%= formatted_date_to_tomorrow(@campaign.event.weekend_4_dates) %>
		</h3>
		<ul class="page_data">
			<li>Implement follow-up strategy (Appendix D, F)
				<ul>
					<li>Letter to attendees within two days of the Gathering (Appendix D)</li>
					<li>Call to attendees to thank and encourage early participation</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>Track advance commitments as they come in</li>
			<li>Send thank you notes to those who make their commitment early. The thank you notes should come from the pastor</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div> <!-- END PAGE 5 -->

<!-- PAGE 6 -->
<div id="page_6" class="print-page" data-mercury="full">
	<hr><%= image_tag get_image_path, :alt => 'logo', :class => 'logo' %>
	<h2><%= formatted_date_to_tomorrow(@campaign.event.weekend_4_dates) %></h2>
	<h3>Commitment Weekend</h3>
	<ul class="page_data">
		<li>Plan to attend Mass this weekend. Do not neglect the privilege of worshiping this week! If you have not done so, prayerfully complete your commitment card</li>
		<li>Continue to support your parish and the campaign in your own prayers</li>
	</ul>
	<br>
	<h2><%= formatted_date_to_tomorrow(@campaign.event.celebration_mass_dates) %></h2>
	<h3>Attend a Celebration Weekend Mass</h3>
	<br><br>
	<h5><em>"Thank you for making a difference in the life of your parish and in the success of this campaign."</em></h5>
</div>